title: OvercomingAddiction.pdf
description: This is an ebook I wrote in 2007 about overcoming addictions. I am offering it free in the hopes that it may help people. I struggled with addictions for over twenty-five years before overcoming it. This is not a commercial product, nor an upsell product, nor is it anything other than a sincere gift to anyone who may appreciate it. You are free to distribute it, but do not modify it.
